#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><h2>
#: template.html:58
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "What’s New in Wesnoth 1.12"
msgid "What’s New in This Update"
msgstr "韦诺之战 1.12 新增元素"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><p>
#: template.html:60
msgid ""
"In the three-and-a-half years since version 1.12, we on the development team "
"have dedicated much thought towards the future of Wesnoth and where we want "
"to take the game going forward. Consequently, this version lays the "
"groundwork for new and exciting changes, some of which are included here, "
"and some of which we hope to unveil further down the line. Dozens of "
"contributors dedicated hundreds of hours modernizing our engine, improving "
"the interface, adding new content, and streamlining the player experience to "
"ensure this version of Wesnoth is the most stable we have ever released. A "
"huge number of long-standing bugs were squashed, a brand new solo campaign "
"was added along with nine new multiplayer maps, and a brand new multiplayer "
"lobby and revamped add-on manager make their debut!"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><p>
#: template.html:62
msgid ""
"Probably most notable of all, in order to reach a greater audience and "
"expand our frontiers, this is also the first release to be published on the "
"<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/599390\"><b>Steam Store</b></"
"a>, available for free on Windows, macOS, and Linux platforms! This is "
"something many people have requested over the years, and we hope it brings "
"new faces to our community."
msgstr ""

